                <a
                    href="https://www.ewg.org/consumer-guides/healthy-living-home-guide"
                    >Sustainable Living Tips</a
                >
            </li>
            <li data-aos="fade-up">
              <a href="https://climate.nasa.gov/climate_resources/"
                  >Understanding Climate Change</a
              >
          </li>
          <li data-aos="fade-up">
              <a
                  href="https://www.investopedia.com/articles/investing/092815/impact-investing.asp"
                  >Investing in Green Technologies</a
