      </ul>

      <h2 data-aos="fade-up">Join the Community</h2>
      <p data-aos="fade-up">
          Connect with like-minded individuals in our community forums. Share your
          experiences, ask questions, and collaborate on projects aimed at making
          the world a greener place.
      </p>
      <p data-aos="fade-up">
          <a href="https://www.reddit.com/r/sustainability/"
              >Join the Community Forums</a
          >
      </p>
